{"id": 1936, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今，你见过哪些不真实的反叛？", "description": "一种为了叛逆而叛逆的叛逆。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 9446, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170930112705yUtFOMJ8qcaCAw2P.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-29T17:00:30Z", "questions": [{"id": 3058, "title": "现如今，你见过哪些不真实的反叛？", "content": "现如今，你见过哪些不真实的反叛？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 238931, "content": "歌手参加节目时候的表演型不屑，大多数人battle完了会互相致谢", "image": "img/option/option/201709291815453aF1o9y6nPl8U4kB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 238947, "content": "民谣歌手或者明星的“忧郁不羁，不愿搭理整个世界”人设", "image": "img/option/option/20170929183002FkH2ES4Ihprnx6c5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 238948, "content": "汽车、摩托车、旅行等产品的广告里时不时拿“再不冲动一回就老了”说事", "image": "img/option/option/20170929190007C0NQZo8m4OPGxMlq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 238932, "content": "年轻人创业者在宣传中尤其强调反叛和不羁，其实循规蹈矩，没啥称得上反叛的", "image": "img/option/option/20170929190231x6yCS3fkPMi1AVcK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 238955, "content": "职场上表现得桀骜不驯拒绝管束，并且不做琐碎的工作", "image": "img/option/option/20170929190328a9Zb7j2il0peBAHP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 238938, "content": "动不动酒醉街头，发疯发痴，缅怀青春之逝去，假装离经叛道", "image": "img/option/option/20170929190633yRwEImBGKoMCihJZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}